data.description: Beautiful neighborhood in a very desirable area of Melbourne.  This unit is located in the best spot in the community.  Just to the right of the entrance gate, only 1 unit separation from the pool, so close it's like your own personal pool, Awesome water views from your back slider and very close and convenient to the shops, restaurants and grocery stores.  No need to worry about the roof because it was replaced this year 2023. Also, low expenses as the HOA fee covers many things including Cable, Internet, Pest Control, Landscaping, and much more.  Just come in and relax and enjoy. This unit will be professionally cleaned and Ionized prior to closing.  Please call Agent if you have any questions.
